---
title: Veggie Loaded Kale & Risoni Soup with Homemade Garlic Bread
description: We love warm and hearty soups that make us feel cosy and nurtured, just like this flavoursome bowl of goodness. Packed with veggies and risoni and teamed with an easy side of garlic bread, it’s a sure-fire cure for any winter blues.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d2fef027ac6d4000e16d931-4cb38a47.jpg
